            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Pick up a stone. Choose any willing creature, including yourself, to cast a spell and enchant the stone with the spell. Track how much mana was cast with the spell. At any time, you may use the stone to cast the associated spell as a consumable, following the same rules as scrolls. The stone lasts until the end of your next long rest.",
